"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Lightning as an aspect of heavy rain storms</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:23-Exod9:24\">EXO 9:23–9:24</a></p>\n<h2>Lightning as a symbol</h2>\n<h3>A symbol of the power of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:30-Job36:33\">JOB 36:30–36:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:13\">2SA 22:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:15\">2SA 22:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:3\">JOB 37:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:11\">JOB 37:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:15\">JOB 37:15</a>JOB <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:24\">38:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:35\">JOB 38:35</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:12-Ps18:14\">PSA 18:12–18:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:18\">PSA 77:18</a>PSA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:48\">78:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:32\">PSA 105:32</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:4\">PSA 97:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:7\">PSA 135:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:6\">PSA 144:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:12-Jer10:13\">JER 10:12–10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:18\">REV 16:18</a></p>\n<h3>A symbol of brightness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:3\">MAT 28:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:29\">LUK 9:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:10\">EZK 21:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:15\">EZK 21:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:28\">EZK 21:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:6\">DAN 10:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:11\">HAB 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:14\">ZEC 9:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:4\">LUK 24:4</a></p>\n<h2>Lightning as ``fire from heaven''</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:16\">JOB 1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:10-2Kgs1:12\">2KI 1:10–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:54\">LUK 9:54</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:9\">REV 20:9</a></p>\n<h2>Lightning as a sign of the presence of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:16\">EXO 19:16</a></strong> <em>At Mount Sinai</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:5\">REV 4:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:18\">EXO 20:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:4\">EZK 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:13-Ezek1:14\">EZK 1:13–1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:5\">REV 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:19\">REV 11:19</a></p>\n<h2>Lightning used metaphorically</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:27\">MAT 24:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:24\">LUK 17:24</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:5\">HOS 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:4\">NAM 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:18\">LUK 10:18</a></p>",
